messages.message:
Does anyone have any quick pain points regarding data on our platform? Specifically for the task of getting and using data from a customer, especially from POCs. Here is some feedback I got so far from others:
- Actually getting the data and sending data over email with the customer
- Handling multiple datasets and different versions of data over time
- Sending/compiling the results of some process for some dataset
- Viewing the overall OCR quality of some intake documents
- Having a standardized way to load, process, and test/evaluate the results of a dataset
